public static java.util.Comparator<java.lang.Object> getComparator(org.openrdf.model.URI u)
Returns a comparator depending on the input URI. Currently supported datatypes: decimal (and all subdatatypes), boolean, float, double, string If the input URI matches none of them, then we fall back on an extended version of the SPARQL order by comparator.
